items.sentence: I can\'t make that decision without talking to Tom first.
I could have won the race if I hadn\'t sprained my ankle.
I didn\'t know Tom and Mary were planning to get married.
The doctors told Tom that Mary didn\'t have long to live.
Tom doesn\'t seem to want to have anything to do with me.
Tom doesn\'t think Mary and I can take care of ourselves.
Tom doesn\'t think Mary is saying what she really thinks.
Sorry I couldn\'t come over yesterday. Something came up.
I hear you\'re selling your car. What do you want for it?
I think that I should probably change my profile picture.
